# Prompt Examples

## Education & Study

- "Explain photosynthesis for school students in simple words."
- "Give me important questions on digital electronics with answers."
- "Summarize this chapter in bullet points."
- "Explain Newton's Laws with real-life examples."
- "Create 10 quiz questions on computer networks."

## Communication

- "Write a professional leave email."
- "Improve this sentence to sound more confident."
- "Write a polite message asking for assignment extension."
- "Write a thank you email after an interview."
- "Correct the grammar in this paragraph."

## Coding & Debugging

- "Write a Python program to find prime numbers with explanation."
- "Explain loops in Java for beginners."
- "Find the error in this code and explain how to fix it."
- "Write a C program to check whether a number is even or odd."
- "Explain the difference between list and tuple in Python."

## Story & Creative Writing

- "Write a short story about a student who creates an AI robot."
- "Give me a motivational caption for a travel photo."
- "Write a poem about friendship in simple words."
- "Write a funny story about a cat that wants to become a teacher."
- "Create a short horror story set in a haunted school."

## Art & Design Prompts

- "Generate a futuristic city illustration with neon lights."
- "Create a logo idea for an AI startup."
- "Suggest a color palette for a modern portfolio website."
- "Design a poster for an environmental awareness campaign."
- "Create a minimal app UI idea for a fitness tracker."

## Speech & Interview Practice

- "Give me common HR interview questions with sample answers."
- "Act as an interviewer and ask me Java technical questions."
- "Help me prepare a speech on the importance of technology."
- "Give me a self-introduction for an interview."
- "Ask me coding interview questions for Python."

## Productivity & Daily Use

- "Create a daily study timetable for a college student."
- "Help me plan my tasks for the week."
- "Suggest ways to improve time management."
- "Create a morning routine for students."
- "Help me make a weekly workout schedule."

